### ✅ Key Design Decisions

| Aspect | Choice | Rationale |
|--------|--------|-----------|
| Storage | Columnar + mmap | Selective column loading (44% I/O savings), zero-copy access |
| Dates | int32_t (epoch days) | Compact (4B), fast comparisons, no parsing overhead |
| Decimals | int64_t (scale 100) | Precision without IEEE 754 rounding errors |
| Strings | Dictionary encoding | 90% space savings for low-cardinality (3–7 values) |
| Sort Order | lineitem.l_shipdate | Primary filter in all 3 queries, improves zone map effectiveness |
| Indexes | Zone maps + hash | Range pushdown (Q6: 97% I/O reduction), join acceleration |
| Parallelism | OpenMP for indexes | 64 cores available; zone maps parallelized per-block |

